- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is a possibility as the title mentions "distributed information processing systems".
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is a possibility as the paper mentions the use of a mathematical model to formalize semantics.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility as the paper describes the SysLab system model as an abstract mathematical model for information systems and their components.
